The pants are never long enough (to the GROUND not my ankles!!) and the sleeves of the shirts don't come out long enough. How many times have I dragged his ass up those stairs, holding his hand- him tripping each time?) So the story- the scarecrow scared Mike when he was little. Yeah. Lolz.

event,"

I don't know what's wrong with me. I hate when life does this. So this whole Mike thing is STILL eating at me. One second I'm fine and dandy the next I'm in tears on the floor. I was OFF THE WALL today. I didn't see Mike at all and I didn't mind. I was HAPPY and enjoying everything. Then I watched Joan of Arcaidia. And it made me cry. I want to throw Mike against a locker and kiss him. I want to slap him. I want to scream in his face I HATE YOU!!!!!!! I want to whisper in his ear- How Hard Is It To Keep A Promise? If I hadn't promised ""Joran""... JORAN! HA! Wow, what a joke. I thought he was the best thing to happen to me. Then I made the biggest mistake of my life by calling. NO. Mike was the best- no. That night was the best thing to happen to me. I held everything anyone could ever want in the palm of my hand, with my hot pink nails, tingling at the touch of his skin. I put my hands on his face and looked into his eyes. He took them off and put them on his shoulders. I kissed him. I kissed him. It was like finding perfect in a bottle, that I lost in the back of my closet barried under clothes that haven't fit in forever. I stumbled upon this bottle, so pretty and wonderful in its dusty and old glory. This ugly tainted object, holding all this amazing-ness. And then I dropped it on the floor. Like the sea monkeys when I was 7. Gone. And all the tears, and blood shed for nothing. Although no blood spilled for you. I thought maybe, just maybe you were- HA!- keeping your promise. ""I won't hurt you."" ""Promise"" Lier lier lier lier. I hate you for that. I see you looking at me in the hall way, you're eyes watch me. Half the time I can't look at you. I did yestrday. And I almost died. You're eyes are so blue. I never noticed. Just how small they are. I know I go on about this. I know it never ends. I'm boy crazy and stupid and ugly and pudgy and annoying. And bitchy- who could forget that? My number one trait- RIGHT LISSA? CAUSE YOU'RE ALWAYS SO DAMN RIGHT. Leave me alone. All of you. Chris beats his girlfriends? Mike isn't talking to me? Dave is all my fault? Joran is a LIE? Lauren had sex with Simon? Just back the hell off. I swear to God, this smile is painted and these words are lies. I hold my breath and kiss the cars goodbye. I walk in the middle of the streat and pray. Not to make it out alive. For an IV and a hospital bed and you holding my hand. Yes, we'll see who loves me then. ""Becca's dead."" Who's going to cry? You? No. Why would you? I'm a bitch and a fake. I'M 15! I'M NOT PERFECT AND NO ONE IS. I AM SSSSSSSSSOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO SORRY FOR EVERYTHING BUT THE ONE THING I'M NOT SORRY FOR IS KISSING HIM. I will never take that back. Because I know what happy is. THAT is happy. HE is happy. You don't have to understand it. I don't either. I never will. I don't get life. I really don't. One second I have it all. Then I lose it cause I open my mouth. You're sorry you even bothered. SO AM I. Somehow this is all my fault.... I'm not really all to sure how that happened. I don't want to sit here and figure it out though. I am so over this. I am going to live my life and not let you or anyone else hold me down. I know... never mind. That would be almost as beautiful a lie as he tells. I know who I am. Does anyone really ever know that? I mean, honestly. I don't think so. And I think all of you are as messed up as me. It's just so much easier to blame other people for what we're too scared to open our eyes and find out that it had to happen and it's no ones fault. Because it always is. We're just stupid. My life is your life on fastforward or rewind, depending who you are. Your life is my life on fastforward or rewind, depending who you are. So the bible was wrong- we are all the same. So go kiss the guy you like and fall in love with a lie. Then come tell me I'm dramatic and stupid and a bitch. This is not what I wanted to happen. But it did. So shoot me. I know you want too. ""Pull the trigger... and the nightmare.... stops...""

"

event,"SO- Pete from Fall Out Boy has an lj. my oh my. Some part of me wants him to stumble upon this journal and read my words and want to be my friend. Want to talk to me. Want to know where these beautiful thoughts come from. I wonder that about him. It's hard to think someone like him is a person. Thru and thru he is just like you and I. I totally admire him. Finch never updates their page and here FOB has a LJ and myspace and put the cell number up. They are so devoted to the fans. I want to be more than a FAN tho. I want to be Becca. That girl. That one, you know, the one who sees us as more than some hot guys in a band and our music as more than sound. That one, that girl. Becca. Funny how all this FOB stuff is happening. I want to go to the concert so bad and my cousin is trying so hard to find a way to make it work. Maybe Kaliegh can come with me. I want her too, we'd have fun. Oh yeah, and the Fall Out Boy guy wore his FOB t-shirt today. I want to go out with him. He's so admirable.

SO- Today was WILD. I started out in my skirt and black panty hose and boots. 3ed- my hose ripp. between 3-4- i take them off. after 4- switch into my vans. only my legs arnt shaved, so between RC and lunch, i put on pants. all day people were like, ""weren't you wearing something else?"" lolz. Then at the end of the day I talked to Chris and asked him what he should have talked to me about. Only he said I don't remember like Mike always did when I remembered something he didnt want me to know to begin with. So I said ""come on, just make something up."" Then he says: ""OH! YEAH! So I had this bunny and i tried to feed him only he wouldn't eat cabbige and carrots so I took him to the vet and the vet said he's gay and I'm like so, gay bunnys still eat cabbige and carrots and he goes no, the eat peanut butter so I take him home and feed him peanut butter only he got all sticky and couldnt open his mouth so he suffocated and died."" Never again will I tell Chris to make something up. Oh my god it was so funny. Then he walks away and I tell Jelena I want to date him and she says sorry. I give her my tangerine and she spits the seads everywhere and I look down the hall and some kid is flicking his coat around like somethings on it, only he looks overjoyed at this. So I'm like, ""having fun with your coat over there buddy?"" and he goes, ""No. But one day it came alive."" Jelena goes, ""your friends are weird"" and I'm like, ""I dont even know that kid!!"" and he goes ""why are you talking to me then?"" and i say, ""Cause I'm like that."" and he goes ""So am i!"" and flicks his coat at me. It was crazy. Ah- and lame ass Becca in French class: Thursday. total blank. Sing the song. ""I can't get past Monday""
